    <item>
      <title>Winklevoss 双胞胎的 Gemini 将支付 500 万美元以结束 CFTC 案件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/winklevoss-twins-gemini-to-pay-5-million-fine-to-end-cftc-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[文克莱沃斯双胞胎兄弟的 Gemini Trust Co. 加密货币交易所同意支付 500 万美元，以结束美国商品期货交易委员会的诉讼，该诉讼声称其在推出首个受美国监管的比特币期货合约时误导了衍生品监管机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/winklevoss-twins-gemini-to-pay-5-million-fine-to-end-cftc-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 17:24:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CFPB 起诉伯克希尔旗下的贷款机构，称其贷款“难以承受”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/berkshire-owned-lender-sued-by-cfpb-over-unaffordable-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家最高金融监管机构在周一提起的诉讼中指控称，沃伦·巴菲特的伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司旗下的一家贷款机构故意忽视部分借款人的收入或资产不足，发放了“无法承受”的住房抵押贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/berkshire-owned-lender-sued-by-cfpb-over-unaffordable-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 14:42:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
