    <item>
      <title>特朗普否认削减关税报告后美元缩减跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/dollar-falls-most-in-two-months-on-report-trump-to-limit-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普否认有关他的关税计划不会像最初担心的那样广泛的报道后，美元兑大多数主要货币周一大幅缩减跌幅，汇率波动打击了年初大举做多美元的交易员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/dollar-falls-most-in-two-months-on-report-trump-to-limit-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 12:03:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，Brookfield 的 Clarios 计划举债以支付股息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/brookfield-s-clarios-is-said-to-plan-raising-debt-for-dividend</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Clarios International Inc. 正在考虑承担新债务，以便将现金交给其所有者，包括 Brookfield Asset Management Ltd. 和加拿大养老基金 Caisse de Depot et Placement du Quebec。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/brookfield-s-clarios-is-said-to-plan-raising-debt-for-dividend</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 12:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英伟达股价创历史新高，股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/asian-stocks-set-to-rise-after-wall-street-rebound-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2025 年第一个完整交易周开始时，全球最大科技公司的股价上涨，提振了股市。由于当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示他的关税计划不会缩减，美元缩减了跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/asian-stocks-set-to-rise-after-wall-street-rebound-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 22:31:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
